HOW TO INSTALL RSTAN
1. Install on MacOS
2. Install on BU SCC

MacOS v10.15.4 and R v4.0.0
1. If using macOS, install the package V8: https://github.com/jeroen/V8
2. Install rstan: https://github.com/stan-dev/rstan/wiki/RStan-Getting-Started

BU SCC: Linux CentOS 7.5 and R v4.0.0
This directions install RStan for your personal profile
1. Load R:
$ module load R/4.0.0
2. Open R:
$ R
3. install packages. example of installing rstan:
> install.packages('rstan')
